
Deployment options outside of docker

To run under uWSGI and nginx:
----------------------------
$ uwsgi -s /tmp/hexhub.sock --virtualenv /path/to/virtual/environment /Users/swat/dev/hexagram/hub/venv --manage-script-name --mount /=hub:app
#$ uwsgi -s /tmp/yourapplication.sock --manage-script-name --mount /yourapplication=myapp:app

Additional python libraries over what we need for the python calc scripts:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
- conda:
    - flask
- deploy with uWSGI and nginx: pip:
    - uwsgi
- deploy with fastcgi and nginx: pip:
    - flask-socketio
    - eventlet
